T02TD3264E:19a-1: mee tri ya s'a dha nam /
T02TD3264E:19a-4: sngar bshad pa'i tshogs zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du yi ge mem ser po yongs su gyur pa las sems dpa'i skyil mo krung gis sna tshogs padma la bzhugs pa /
T02TD3264E:19a-6: spyan gsum phyag bzhi pa g-yas pa dang g-yon pa'i zhal ni nag pa dang dkar ba /
T02TD3264E:19a-8: phyag gnyis kyis chos bshad ba'i phyag rgya mdzad pa /
T02TD3264E:19a-9: g-yas pa dang g-yon pa'i phyag gzhan gnyis kyis ni mchog sbyin pa dang /
T02TD3264E:19a-10: me tog rgyas pa'i klu shing gi yal ga mdzes pa bsnams pa /
T02TD3264E:19a-11: sna tshogs pa'i rgyan dang ldan pa'i byams pa'i skur bdag nyid dmigs la phyag rgya bcing bar bya ste /
T02TD3264E:19a-12: lag pa gnyis kyi sor mo khu tshur bsdams la mdzub mo gnyis mthe bong dag gi dbus su mchog tu gnas pas me tog gi rnam pa ltar gshibs pa'o //
T02TD3264E:19a-13: de nas bzlas pa bya ste /
T02TD3264E:19a-14: aom mem mee tri ya sv'a h'a /
T02TD3264E:19b-1: pandi ta chen po shanta dang aa bha ya las dge slong tshul khrims rgyal mtshan gyis bsgyur ba'o//
